<TEXT>
a us soldier was killed when a 
truck he was riding in lost its brakes and crashed in eastern saudi 
arabia the us military said sunday 
the soldier was the 47th member of the us armed forces to die 
during operation desert shield since deployment began aug 7 five 
days after iraq invaded kuwait most of the deaths have been in 
accidents 
